original_title: The Seekers Farewell: The Golden Jubilee Australian Farewell Tour
overview: Documentary coverage of the 2013 farewell tour of the legendary Australian folk/pop group The Seekers, including their final public performances.
tagline: Fifty years on, The Seekers are still touching the hearts and souls of fans around the world.
title: The Seekers Farewell: The Golden Jubilee Australian Farewell Tour
